These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-1::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: tram, car, trike
There are 3 different nationalities: indonesian, british, russian
1. the person driving the tram is in an even position##4
2. the indonesian is on the left or right of the russian##3
3. the indonesian is the person driving the car##1
4. the person driving the trike is on the far left##1
5. the british is the british##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |      1      |      2      |     3     |
| Transport   | trike | tram | car |
| Nationality    | british    | russian | indonesian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-2::.
House: palace, modern, art-deco
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: soccer, ice-hockey, rowing
1. the palace house is on the far right##1
2. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is in an even position##4
3. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the art-deco house##1
4. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| House       | modern | art-deco | palace |
| Sport   | rowing    | ice-hockey     | soccer        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-3::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: may, march, january
There are 3 different favourite beverages: fanta, sprite, juice
1. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
2. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
3. the person who's birthday is in march is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3    |
| Birthday         | january     | march | may |
| Beverage   | sprite | fanta     | juice  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-4::.
There 3 different types of food: watermelon, strawberry, apple
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, tiparillo, havana
1. the person eating strawberry is the tiparillo-smoker##1
2. the person eating watermelon is the havana-smoker##1
3. the person eating strawberry is in an even position##4
4. the person eating strawberry is on the right of the person eating apple##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3     |
| Food   | apple | strawberry  | watermelon  |
| Cigar         | prince  | tiparillo | havana |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-5::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: purple, brown, coral
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: superhero, comedy, thriller
1. the person who likes coral is between the person who likes purple and the person watching superhero movies##2
2. the person who likes brown is in an odd position##4
3. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |    3     |
| Color         | purple   | coral | brown    |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy | thriller     | superhero |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-6::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: quad-bike, jet-ski, train
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: poppy, daffodil, bellflower
1. the person driving the quad-bike is the person who growsdaffodil##1
2. the person who growsbellflower is the person driving the jet-ski##1
3. the person driving the jet-ski is in an odd position##4
4. the person driving the train is on the right of the person who growsbellflower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |    3     |
| Transport   | jet-ski | train | quad-bike   |
| Flower   | bellflower     | poppy    | daffodil |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-7::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: baking, drawing, chess
There are 3 different favourite colors: red, lavender, lilac
1. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1
2. the person who's hobby is baking is between the person who likes lilac and the person who's hobby is chess##2
3. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
4. the person who likes red is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |   3    |
| Hobby   | chess | baking | drawing |
| Color           | lavender         | red         | lilac |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-8::.
House: futuristic, ranch-style, wooden
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: march, july, november
1. the person who's birthday is in march is between the person who's birthday is in july and the futuristic house##2
2. the person who's birthday is in november is in an odd position##4
3. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the wooden house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |  2   |     3     |
| House   | ranch-style | wooden | futuristic |
| Birthday    | july    | march | november     |

