.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-9::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: turquise, amber, light-blue
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: daisy, begonia, balloon-flower
1. the person who growsballoon-flower is in an odd position##4
2. the person who growsbegonia is on the left of the person who likes turquise##1
3. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left of the person who likes amber##1
4. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left or right of the person who growsbegonia##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |
| Color   | light-blue   | amber  | turquise  |
| Flower         | balloon-flower | begonia | daisy |

