.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-11::.
3 different pets are kept: cat, dog, horse
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: pop, r&b, classical
1. the owner of the horse is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
2. the fan of pop is the owner of the cat##1
3. the fan of classical is the owner of the horse##1
4. the owner of the horse is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2    |     3      |
| Pet         | dog | horse | cat |
| Music-Genre   | r&b | classical   | pop |

