.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-12::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: reading, magic-tricks, hiking
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: house, salsa, techno
1. the fan of techno is on the right of the fan of house##1
2. the person who's hobby is reading is the fan of techno##1
3. the fan of salsa is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##3
4. the fan of techno is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3      |
| Hobby   | hiking | magic-tricks | reading |
| Music-Genre     | salsa     | house   | techno        |

