.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-13::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: thriller, crime, western
House: craftsman, futuristic, townhouse
1. the townhouse house is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
2. the craftsman house is the person watching crime movies##1
3. the person watching western movies is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |
| Movie-Genre   | western  | thriller | crime   |
| House         | futuristic | townhouse   | craftsman |

