.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-14::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cricket, basketball, golf
There 3 different types of food: grapes, pineapple, corn
1. the person who's sport is golf is between the person who's sport is basketball and the person eating pineapple##2
2. the person who's sport is basketball is in an odd position##4
3. the person eating pineapple is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the person eating grapes##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |   3    |
| Sport   | basketball | golf | cricket |
| Food     | grapes    | corn  | pineapple   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-15::.
3 different games are played: whist, backgammon, scrabble
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, montecristo, old-henry
1. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the person playing whist##1
2. the montecristo-smoker is on the left of the bongani-smoker##1
3. the montecristo-smoker is on the left or right of the person playing scrabble##3
4. the person playing scrabble is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3    |
| Game   | whist  | scrabble     | backgammon |
| Cigar   | montecristo | bongani | old-henry    |

