.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-18::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: van, quad-bike, bus
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, baccarat, fonseca
1. the fonseca-smoker is on the right of the person driving the van##1
2. the person driving the van is in the middle##1
3. the person driving the bus is the baccarat-smoker##1
4. the aristoff-smoker is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3     |
| Transport         | bus | van   | quad-bike |
| Cigar   | baccarat   | aristoff | fonseca      |

