.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-19::.
3 different pets are kept: ferret, goldfish, guinea-pig
House: townhouse, futuristic, ranch-style
1. the ranch-style house is on the left or right of the owner of the ferret##3
2. the owner of the ferret is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
4. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the townhouse house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |    3     |
| Pet      | ferret | goldfish | guinea-pig |
| House   | futuristic   | ranch-style          | townhouse |

