.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-20::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: grey, apricot, yellow
The people have 3 different hobbies: sudoku, fishing, camping
1. the person who's hobby is camping is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the person who likes yellow##1
3. the person who likes yellow is in an even position##4
4. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person who likes apricot##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2     |     3      |
| Color     | apricot  | yellow   | grey |
| Hobby   | camping | fishing | sudoku       |

 